      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SCOTT SIGMA (1) jumped from the inside and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 1.3 lengths (30.63) behind Analyzation at The Meadows. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and four minor placings to her credit. Well placed and gets her chance. ZIPPING COLUMBUS (3) wasn't far away at the finish when 4th and beaten only one length (30.10) at The Meadows. Goes very well here at the trip finding the frame in each of three starts. Won at his only start from this draw. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. PAW ISLA (8) is an honest type in the frame at six of 14 starts including six wins, the latest scoring (30.32) over 525m at The Meadows. Form at this distance is sound. Has the ability and rates a key chance this line-up. IAN ALBERT (2) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.",
